                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>in my power, hoping that you will believe me<lb/> an <sic>especialy</sic> you may be\n                convinced of the<lb/> truth thereof from <placeName>Memphis</placeName> from\n                        <placeName><sic>davenport</sic></placeName> and<lb/> from here I hope you\n                will do so.</p>\n            <p>Please God next week I will send you money<lb/> for a dozen of your Religious\n                books.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">your most obedient</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">E. Marcuson</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
